data.description: Welcome Home to One of Reedy Fork Ranch's Beautiful Homes! This home features a large open concept on the main level with 9ft ceilings throughout. The home also features a beautiful kitchen with an island and granite countertops. The main level also features an expansive great room and an extra flex room that can be used for an office or whatever the owner desires! Upstairs features 3 bedrooms and loft area which is an entertainers dream! Let's take a journey outside to the backyard which includes a large massive area for grilling or sitting out enjoying on the patio or the large lawn area! The backyard also includes a 6 foot privacy fence. Hurry this home won't last long!
